article_id:758,category_name:News,title_name:Daily Free Tenfold Summon Incoming! Summon Up to 100 Times During the Event!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fdbe5adea960e95742a1c8e3accb617f.png,message:<div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fdbe5adea960e95742a1c8e3accb617f.png"></div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, starts <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcases</div><div>You can perform a tenfold summon on each of the following summon showcases for free once per day.</div><div><br></div><div>・Gala Dragalia</div><div>Note: You can perform up to seven tenfold summons during the seven-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570168740"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>・Fractured Futures</div><div>Note: You can perform up to three tenfold summons during the three-day period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570168800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570427940"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can perform a tenfold summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 07:00 to 06:59 the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free tenfold summon resets each day at 07:00.</div><div>3. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569477600,update_time1574300288